::Bloodystrike::

Bloodystrike jumps as the CR chamber's door blows out, his gun aimed at the 
bot. He relaxes when he hears the bot's speach. So, he thinks to himself, 
another psycho to join in!

"Zardus is busy at the moment," Bloodystrike says calmly, "Would you like a 
tour of the base untill he's free?"
